{"id":"api/core/switch","title":"@switch","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/switch\", \"name\": \"@switch\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/switch.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"switch\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b8dil8mo3zfgak3jt9u8aoica\">@switch<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#switch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label block\">block</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bufqfyzq912hvk1sbdj4016lq\"><code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code>區塊受JavaScript的\n<code>switch</code>語句啟發：</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/switch#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n    <h2 id=\"syntax\">語法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <code-example language=\"html\">\n@switch (condition) {\n  @case (caseA) {\n    Case A.\n  }\n  @case (caseB) {\n    Case B.\n  }\n  @default {\n    Default case.\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eqhfzanxohew8n21qyw92uko6\"><code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code>區塊顯示由對應條件表示式的案例之一選擇的內容。條件表示式的值使用\n<code>===</code>運算符與案例表示式進行比較。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7jrdgrwbq335a8667lw5dxfi6\"><code>@default</code>區塊是可選的，可以省略。如果沒有\n<code>@case</code>對應表示式，並且沒有\n<code>@default</code>區塊，則不顯示任何內容。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"38l6muq3o9lq3vshs8kn1czc0\"><strong><code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code> 沒有 fallthrough，因此不需要等效於 <code>break</code> 或 <code>return</code> 語句。</strong></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/control_flow\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/switch#description\n - api/core/switch#switch\n - api/core/switch#syntax\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/aio/content/blocks/core/switch.md\n-->"}